keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Classifier

Class FuzzyFGPClassifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Classifier.Classifier
      • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Classifier.FuzzyFGPClassifier

  • public class FuzzyFGPClassifier
extends Classifier

    FuzzyFGPClassifier is designed to allow a Fuzzy Classifier evolve by means of an Genetic Programming (GP). This class is a specification of the class Classifier.

    Since:
    JDK1.4

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
